"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-nepathya-to-perform-at-the-seoul-olympic-park\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, Sept 19: Nepal's premier folk rock band is set to travel to South Korea to perform at the Olympic Hall of Seoul Olympic Park.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0526239090355864e-15, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999427104757, \"rank\": 3.651757368392751e-08, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nepathya will perform at the renowned Seoul Olympic Park\\u00a0also known as\\u00a0Olpark is an Olympic Park built to host the 1988 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepathya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nepathya\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepathya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepathya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2011, the Olympic hall was renovated by the Korean Government converting it into a concert hall.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.9940804974748018, \"rank\": 0.005939443203638741, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musicians of international acclaim like Deep Purple, Judas Pr